In Dr. SCheme v.100, from Help->about Dr. Scheme I tried to click on the highlighted link;
after a while I was waiting, the sistem responded "connection to www.cs.rice.edu, port 80 failed (1:11002 host not found)".
But Rice's site is up and I am connected to it another window. May be the problem comes from the fact that my workstation goes on the internet through a Microsoft proxy server (which is actually configured for every protocol).

